%h2
  API

%p
  To connect to us via HTTP, add `X-CodeLonia-Token` header to your
  requests, with this value (keep it secret):

%p
  %code
    &= token

%p
  Most important entry points:

%ul
  %li
    %code POST /submit?platform=github&coordinates=...
    to submit a new project
  %li
    %code POST /p/123/post?text=...
    to submit a review
  %li
    %code GET /recent.json?page=...
    to list all visible projects
  %li
    %code GET /p/123.json?page=...
    to list all reviews per project

%p
  If something doesn't work,
  %a{href: 'https://github.com/denistreshchev/CodeLonia'}
    submit a ticket
  to GitHub.
